<TEXT>
<P>
(By Wang Jinyu and Liu Zongya)
</P>
<P>
NAIROBI, February 20 (Xinhua) -- Foreign ministers of Kenya,
South Africa and Tanzania has proposed that the UN peace plan for
Zaire be discussed in a Nairobi summit.
</P>
<P>
