<HEADLINE> Netanyahu Meets With Chinese Vice-Premier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, February 20 (Xinhua) -- Israeli Prime Minister
Binyamin Netanyahu today held talks with visiting Chinese
Vice-Premier Li Lanqing on bilateral ties and issues of mutual
interest.
</P>
<P>
