Carlos Menem proposed here today an economic link between member
countries of the Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN)
and some Latin American nations.
</P>
<P>
Addressing a business luncheon in Spanish, President Menem said
he would urge Latin American country leaders to sign a framework
agreement so that a free trade area will exist in the next few
years.
</P>
<P>
