<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chinese, Kazak Presidents Meet in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 21 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
met here this afternoon with Kazakhstan's President Abishevich
Nazarbayev, who is vacationing in China.
</P>
<P>
On behalf of the Kazak government and people, Nazarbayev
expressed his profound sympathies over the death of Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
He said that Deng, as the chief architect of China's reform and
opening up, witnessed the realization of his great blueprint
design, and the best way to commemorate Deng is to carry forward
his cause of reform and opening up to the outside world.
</P>
<P>
Expressing his heartfelt appreciation, Jiang said that Deng was
an outstanding leader who held a highly prestigious position in
the eyes of the Party, the army and the people of all ethnic
groups throughout China.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said that Deng was also a great Marxist, proletarian
revolutionary, statesman, military strategist and diplomat, as
well as a long-tested Communist soldier, the chief architect of
China's socialist reform, opening up and modernization drive, and
the father of the theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics.
</P>
<P>
The death of Deng is an immeasurable loss for the Party, the
army and the people of all ethnic groups across China, he said.
</P>
<P>
The CPC, the Chinese army and people of various ethnic groups
are determined to turn grief into strength, hold high the great
banner of Deng's theory to build socialism with Chinese
characteristics, unite and continue the great cause of socialist
reforms and opening up and modernization drive unswervingly and
confidently, Jiang said, adding that "we would run China's
undertakings still better, and make greater contributions to the
cause of peace, development and progress of the mankind."
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Jiang said that in the five years of
bilateral diplomatic ties, Sino-Kazak relations in various fields
have developed rapidly and still have great potential for
development, and the frequent exchanges of visits between leaders
of the two sides have enhanced mutual friendship and understanding.
</P>
<P>
He noted that to develop long-term and stable friendship and
cooperation with Kazakhstan is an important component of China's
policy on developing good-neighborly friendship.
</P>
<P>
"We are ready to strengthen cooperation with Kazakhstan in
various fields, in a bid to build a partnership of overall
cooperation, oriented to the next century, between China and
Kazakhstan," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
Nazarbayev said that Jiang's visit to Kazakhstan last year was
"historic," and laid a foundation for bilateral friendship and
cooperation. The Kazak government supports China's foreign policy
and opposes any action of national separatism, he added.
</P>
<P>
He noted that there is vast potential for bilateral economic
cooperation, and the two sides can further strengthen cooperation
in the fields of communications, energy and trade.  
</P>
</TEXT>
