is being collected today.
</P>
<P>
But the workers threatened to down tools again if their
demands are not met.
</P>
<P>
On Thursday Local Government and Housing Minister Bennie
Mwiinga warned the striking workers to call off their stoppage
within 10 days or face dismissals.
</P>
<P>
