</P>
<P>
The Frenchman completed the race with a time of one minute
15.32 seconds.
</P>
<P>
Hermann Maier of Austria finished second in 1:15.87 and Italy's
Werner Perathoner came third in 1:15.90.
</P>
<P>
Ed Podivinsky of Canada was fourth and Kjetil-Andre Aamodt of
Norway took fifth place.
</P>
<P>
Alphand topped the Super Giant Slalom standings with 837 points
and Aamodt was second with 786 points. 
