<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, February 20 (Xinhua) -- Danish Prime Minister Poul
Nyrup Rasmussen and Norwegian Foreign Secretary Jan Egeland have
expressed their sorrow over the death of Chinese leader Deng
Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
Rasmussen said he learned with great sorrow that Deng Xiaoping,
leader of China since 1978, died Wednesday at the age of 93.
</P>
<P>
